A general advise I could give you is that you always install the following frameworks upon a clean install of Windows:
1) .NET 4.5 redistributable framework;
2) C++ 2005 redistributable framework;
3) Java runtime;
4) DirectX 10.0c or 11.

Make sure you have installed those. Rare errors could be depending upon missing one of it.

But you have to be more specific what errors you get please.

